title: TEMPLATE Miniature nightstand with rattan imitation in 1:12 scale | PDF
description: To make the nightstand, you will need a wooden sheet 1.5 mm thick (wooden popsicle sticks), a wooden veneer sheet 0.6 mm thick, tapestry fabric for embroidery, wooden skewers 3 mm in diameter, tacky glue, a ruler, a knife or nippers, a nail file or sandpaper, raw sienna acrylic paint, and brown or black acrylic paint.
